      "dims" : "{"12580446":"四季青小彭","0":"","12016582":"嘉兴市秀洲区洪合锦悦毛衫经营部的小店"}"
    },
    {
      "dimtype" : "logistic",
      "dims" : "{"":"","YTO":"圆通速递","STO":"申通E物流"}"
    },
    {
      "dimtype" : "exception",
      "dims" : "{"1":"即将超时","2":"已超时"}"
    },
    {
      "dimtype" : "orderstatus",
      "dims" : "{"question":"0","sent":"0","":"0","cancelled":"0","delivering":"0"}"
    }
  ],
  "success" : true,
  "msg" : null,
  "act" : 0,
  "total" : 0
}

<br>
--查询SQL示意
select
  string\_agg\(distinct\(warehouse\_name\)\,'\,'\) as warehouse\_name\,
  string\_agg\(distinct\(logistic\_company\_name\)\,'\,'\) as logistic\_company\_name\,
  string\_agg\(distinct\(platform\_name\)\,'\,'\) as platform\_name\,
  string\_agg\(distinct\(shop\_name\)\,'\,'\) as shop\_name\,
  string\_agg\(distinct\(exception\_type\)\,'\,'\) as exception\_type\,
  string\_agg\(distinct\(paid\_order\_status\)\,'\,'\) as paid\_order\_status\,
  from <span class="colour" style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0)">dwd\_jst\_erp\_lgst\_alarm\_detail\_ri</span>
where  co_id = '$coid'
AND warehouse_id IN ()
AND \(shop\_id in \(\) or shop\_id in \(\)\)

AND pay\_time \>= '' and pay\_time <= ''
AND send\_time \>= '' and send\_time <= ''
AND platform_name in ()
AND is_Ignore = ''

\-\- 逻辑说明
1\. 后端每次查询发起都需要查询用户店铺权限，分销商权限及发货仓权限 作为固定过滤条件\,防止越权
2\. 名字类信息如店铺名称，仓库名称存在改名的情况可能一次查询里含有一个店铺的多个名字\,用户通过多选的形式过滤即可
3\. 枚举类字段及名称定义:
  时间类型 - 发货时间,支付时间;
  异常类型 -
  订单处理状态 -
  忽略标记 -
  查询周期 - 昨天至今天 - ; 近7天 - ; 近30天 - ;
